{"tid":871935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人畀人問候老母時嘅反應","createTime":"2018-10-22T10:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T12:16:12.000Z","uid":25643,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f7cb9af3d1064d1cac75ffbd043a57974437d0","tid":871935,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"當香港人畀人問候老母時﹐<br />\n<br />\n會嘗試解釋其實我老母好好㗎﹐<br />\n<br />\n佢十八代祖先係乜乜公主嚟﹐<br />\n<br />\n佢又有啲好好嘅地方﹐<br />\n<br />\n所以我決定認我老母做老母﹐保護我老母。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個老母就係廣東話<br />\n<br />\n香港人根本就唔覺得保護母語係理所當然<br />\n<br />\n畀人屌兩嘢就搬一大堆嘢出嚟辯護<br />\n<br />\n話咩傳承古漢語呀﹐讀詩押韻呀<br />\n<br />\n反映自己心底根本對粵語自卑<br />\n<br />\n覺得唔訴諸呢啲古董就唔理直氣壯<br />\n<br />\n由細到大養育嘅語言都要搵理由支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n母語本身就係唯一理由"},{"pid":"5df7e6aebef650a7b37cd70f31512c7918e5dc95","tid":871935,"uid":25643,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"跟住仲有班港豬走出嚟﹐<br />\n<br />\n話隔離屋老母好疊水﹐<br />\n<br />\n不如我哋同自己老母斷絕關係﹐<br />\n<br />\n過契去隔離屋有錢啲競爭力好啲﹐<br />\n<br />\n講完完全面不紅耳不赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71055026c8e489961c8ad5613821daba83d1571d","tid":871935,"uid":12348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"正皮不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fc632aec61c8c8a01554e5b519fb166979a39d","tid":871935,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21ebe2ef19d700976747b8815f62dee5c098d34","tid":871935,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:15:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/871365/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/871365/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3da4b2f5a69cd2a94daab3572afd3f8910a2d6e1","tid":871935,"uid":155818